  "id" : "api/core/TemplateRef",
  "title" : "TemplateRef",
  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"templateref\">TemplateRef</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label class\">class</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\">@angular/core</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a> } from <a href=\"api/core\">'@angular/core'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/src/linker/template_ref.ts#L11-L41\">core/src/linker/template_ref.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  <section class=\"class-overview\">\n<h2 id=\"overview\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3ivgu86loww6mg4fq1brezlnd\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>概览</h2>\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\nclass <a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a>&lt;C&gt; {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/TemplateRef#elementRef\">get elementRef: ElementRef</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/TemplateRef#createEmbeddedView\">createEmbeddedView(context: C): EmbeddedViewRef&lt;C&gt;</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bpv4mt4e60nzqu7qr8ec21ktl\">表示一个可用于实例化嵌入式视图的嵌入式模板。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"beql17mmu6pj1vebi6s4xoctb\">你可以通过两种方式访问 \n<code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code>。通过放置在 \n<code>&lt;ng-template&gt;</code> 元素（或以 \n<code>*</code> 为前缀的指令）上的指令，并将此嵌入式视图的 \n<code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code> 注入到指令的构造函数中，使用 \n<code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code> 令牌。或者，你可以通过 \n<a href=\"api/core/Query\"><code>Query</code></a> 从组件或指令中查询 \n<code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code>。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3kkw35en3ns40kmqu7beigc9i\">要基于模板实例化嵌入式视图，请使用 \n<a href=\"api/core/ViewContainerRef#\">createEmbeddedView</a>，它将创建视图并将其附加到视图容器。</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"instance-members\">\n  <h2 id=\"members\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e62kgm2ztk7rgk6auybfiv91o\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>成员</h2>\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"elementRef\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">get elementRef: <a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a></code-example>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"azf224xz56xkawnb0rq7ykpy\">嵌入式视图在逻辑上所属的视图中的位置。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6h8jhar4uuj5svrzfmjl3ubgm\">从此 \n<code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code> 创建的嵌入式视图的数据绑定和注入上下文继承自此位置的上下文。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6u7xwv1f5pwzwa2lq109p74ye\">通常，新的嵌入式视图会附加到此位置的视图容器，但在高级用例中，视图可以附加到不同的容器，同时保留来自原始位置的数据绑定和注入上下文。</p>\n\n  </div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"createEmbeddedView\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">createEmbeddedView(context: C): <a href=\"api/core/EmbeddedViewRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">EmbeddedViewRef</a>&lt;C&gt;</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/NgForOf\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/common/NgPluralCase\n - api/common/NgSwitchCase\n - api/common/NgSwitchDefault\n - api/common/NgTemplateOutlet\n - api/core\n - api/core/EmbeddedViewRef\n - api/core/ViewContainerRef\n - guide/structural-directives\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/ElementRef\n - api/core/EmbeddedViewRef\n - api/core/Query\n - api/core/TemplateRef#createEmbeddedView\n - api/core/TemplateRef#description\n - api/core/TemplateRef#elementRef\n - api/core/TemplateRef#members\n - api/core/TemplateRef#overview\n - api/core/TemplateRef#templateref\n - api/core/ViewContainerRef#\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/src/linker/template_ref.ts#L11-L41\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\n-->"
